<note n="0801b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0801b01">自性本不生不滅而今女有生滅之緣故云不守自性</note>
<note n="0801b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0801b02">此句言并本源亦壞絕了不可得也</note>
<note n="0802b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0802b01">善財參具足優婆夷有一小器中藏諸天人等</note>
